{"word":"G5044 - τεκνοτροφέω - teknotrophéō - tek-not-rof-eh'-o - Bring up children","slug":"G5044","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τεκνοτροφέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>teknotrophéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tek-not-rof-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bring up children"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03BA;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C6;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - teknotropheo&#x0304;</b> - <i>tek-not-rof-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5043\">G5043</a> and <a href=\"#/G5142\">G5142</a>; to <i>be a child rearer</i>, that is, <i>fulfil</i> the duties of <i>a female parent:</i> - bring up children."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5040\">G5040</a>, <a href=\"#/G5041\">G5041</a>, <a href=\"#/G5042\">G5042</a>, <a href=\"#/G5043\">G5043</a>"}]}